  sodium: 720 mg
author: Michelle Doll Olson
course: main course
servings: 2
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Italian
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/parmesan-crusted-chicken-5c1aa3fce3f33931fb144f22
